  <p class="abstract"><em>"Vení a San Telmo"</em></p>
  <p class="abstract">Our people are the most important part of San Telmo and we are committed to developing a team through ongoing personal development and training. We work hard, we learn about Argentine cuisine, wine and culture and we have fun doing it.</p>
  <div class="page_break"></div>
